94
00:05:23,026 --> 00:05:23,627
Qian.

95
00:05:23,867 --> 00:05:24,546
Xiang Qian.

96
00:05:24,546 --> 00:05:25,106
Qian.

97
00:05:25,106 --> 00:05:25,947
Why didn't you pick up

98
00:05:25,947 --> 00:05:26,827
