116
00:06:19,267 --> 00:06:20,346
Hey, hey, it's not your fault.

117
00:06:20,346 --> 00:06:21,507
Don't blame yourself.

118
00:06:21,906 --> 00:06:22,827
Now everyone

119
00:06:22,827 --> 00:06:24,106
