120
00:06:27,867 --> 00:06:28,786
There, there.

121
00:06:37,226 --> 00:06:37,947
Who are you looking for?

122
00:06:38,226 --> 00:06:39,226
I'm looking for your boss.

123
00:06:39,827 --> 00:06:40,707
May I know who you are?

124
00:06:40,867 --> 00:06:42,507
On paper, I'm still his father-in-law.

125
00:06:42,747 --> 00:06:43,666
Mr. Jiang is not in.

126
00:06:44,187 --> 00:06:44,906
He's not in?

127
00:06:45,106 --> 00:06:46,106
You didn't even check,

128
00:06:46,106 --> 00:06:47,346
how do you know he's not in?

129
00:06:47,346 --> 00:06:48,147
I'm very sorry.

130
00:06:48,346 --> 00:06:49,666
But I can't let you in.

131
00:06:50,147 --> 00:06:50,827
Why is he so afraid?

132
00:06:51,627 --> 00:06:52,507
Is he scared

133
00:06:52,546 --> 00:06:53,426
that I'd reveal

134
00:06:53,507 --> 00:06:54,747
all the dirty things he did?

135
00:06:54,986 --> 00:06:55,586
Get out of my way!

136
00:06:56,106 --> 00:06:57,106
I'm sorry.

137
00:06:57,106 --> 00:06:57,906
We can't let you in.

138
00:06:57,906 --> 00:06:59,387
Sorry, Mr. Jiang is not in.

139
00:07:00,786 --> 00:07:02,026
He's really not here.

140
00:07:09,627 --> 00:07:10,786
Is he not here

141
00:07:14,307 --> 00:07:15,627
or is he too scared to see me?

142
00:07:16,307 --> 00:07:17,466
Please calm down, sir.

143
00:07:17,747 --> 00:07:18,267
How about this?

144
00:07:18,507 --> 00:07:19,666
If it's something urgent,

145
00:07:19,747 --> 00:07:21,586
