146
00:07:21,786 --> 00:07:22,426
Is that so?

147
00:07:26,466 --> 00:07:26,986
Go!

148
00:07:27,187 --> 00:07:28,106
Tell your boss.

149
00:07:28,507 --> 00:07:29,627
If he won't see me,

150
00:07:29,627 --> 00:07:30,986
I'm going to destroy this place!

151
00:07:31,346 --> 00:07:31,947
No, stop!

152
00:07:32,187 --> 00:07:33,067
Don't do that!

153
00:07:33,786 --> 00:07:34,786
Security!

154
00:07:37,067 --> 00:07:37,947
What are you people doing?

155
00:07:38,147 --> 00:07:39,307
Get Jiang Hongbin out to see me!

156
00:07:39,627 --> 00:07:40,546
Call him here!

157
00:07:41,026 --> 00:07:42,307
Tell him to come see me!

158
00:07:42,507 --> 00:07:43,147
Step aside!

159
00:07:43,426 --> 00:07:44,786
Tell him to come out!

160
00:07:44,947 --> 00:07:46,026
Why are you apprehending me?

161
00:07:46,627 --> 00:07:47,947
You should catch that goon named Jiang!

162
00:07:48,147 --> 00:07:49,106
He's evil!

163
00:07:49,346 --> 00:07:50,786
Let me go! Let me go!

164
00:07:53,546 --> 00:07:54,627
What are you doing?

165
00:07:56,346 --> 00:07:57,426
How could you treat an elder this way?

166
00:07:57,507 --> 00:07:58,307
That's not right.

167
00:07:59,906 --> 00:08:00,586
Leave us.

168
00:08:01,867 --> 00:08:02,747
Sorry about that.

169
00:08:06,707 --> 00:08:07,546
Mr. Xiang.

170
00:08:09,026 --> 00:08:10,267
There's no use making a scene here.

171
00:08:10,426 --> 00:08:11,147
Go home.

172
00:08:13,827 --> 00:08:15,387
