176
00:08:27,106 --> 00:08:28,426
Don't come to the office again.

177
00:08:48,066 --> 00:08:48,507
Dad.

178
00:08:48,786 --> 00:08:49,706
Why are you guys here?

179
00:08:49,786 --> 00:08:50,267
Hang on,

180
00:08:50,267 --> 00:08:51,826
