182
00:08:53,507 --> 00:08:54,387
What are you doing? Have some water.

183
00:08:54,507 --> 00:08:55,786
No, no water.

184
00:08:56,267 --> 00:08:56,786
Listen to me.

185
00:08:56,867 --> 00:08:57,786
I'm not here to make a scene.

186
00:08:58,066 --> 00:08:59,306
I just want to talk to him.

187
00:08:59,666 --> 00:09:00,706
I'm willing to give up our house.

188
00:09:00,906 --> 00:09:01,826
Go ahead and demolish it.

189
00:09:01,987 --> 00:09:02,627
I don't care.

190
00:09:02,906 --> 00:09:03,946
All I'm asking is to give Xiang Nan

191
00:09:04,066 --> 00:09:04,826
back to us.

192
00:09:05,147 --> 00:09:06,347
Give Chai Jin back to us.

193
00:09:06,747 --> 00:09:07,666
Let our family...

194
00:09:07,987 --> 00:09:08,906
He should let our family go.

195
00:09:09,066 --> 00:09:09,906
Give us back our peace.

196
00:09:09,946 --> 00:09:10,706
You think you can resolve this

197
00:09:10,786 --> 00:09:12,026
