198
00:09:12,026 --> 00:09:12,987
Hurry up and take him home.

199
00:09:13,306 --> 00:09:14,026
Come on, let's go.

200
00:09:14,026 --> 00:09:15,426
I didn't think... My only mistake was...

201
00:09:15,467 --> 00:09:15,946
I didn't expect

202
00:09:15,946 --> 00:09:16,867
