203
00:09:17,066 --> 00:09:17,826
Yes, he's shameless.

204
00:09:18,026 --> 00:09:19,107
So there's no point
in reasoning with him.

205
00:09:19,186 --> 00:09:20,467
You're just hurting yourself.

206
00:09:20,627 --> 00:09:21,227
Careful.

207
00:09:31,747 --> 00:09:32,867
You asked for me, Mr. Jiang?

208
00:09:33,946 --> 00:09:34,906
Did my father-in-law

209
00:09:35,066 --> 00:09:35,826
come and make noise

210
00:09:35,867 --> 00:09:36,627
