227
00:10:10,066 --> 00:10:10,826
Chai Jin turned himself in.

228
00:10:11,546 --> 00:10:12,546
He turned himself in?

229
00:10:16,467 --> 00:10:17,107
Also,

230
00:10:17,587 --> 00:10:19,147
