231
00:10:19,706 --> 00:10:21,186
She has the injury report
from the hospital

232
00:10:21,666 --> 00:10:23,066
and a video from that night.

233
00:10:23,227 --> 00:10:24,347
Together with
the previous police report,

234
00:10:25,107 --> 00:10:25,946
it's not

235
00:10:26,627 --> 00:10:27,747
looking good for you.

236
00:10:37,627 --> 00:10:38,227
Okay.

237
00:10:39,066 --> 00:10:39,946
Thanks, Attorney Wu.

238
00:10:40,066 --> 00:10:40,906
Thank you.

239
00:10:42,267 --> 00:10:42,786
Got it.

240
00:10:43,186 --> 00:10:43,747
Bye-bye.

241
00:10:45,786 --> 00:10:46,826
Attorney Wu said

