245
00:10:52,946 --> 00:10:53,627
That's great.

246
00:10:53,627 --> 00:10:54,987
You're finally getting what you want.

247
00:10:56,627 --> 00:10:57,826
But still, we have

248
00:10:57,867 --> 00:10:58,747
