271
00:11:39,786 --> 00:11:41,706
I had the feeling
that he wasn't the type

272
00:11:42,147 --> 00:11:42,987
who would get married

273
00:11:43,026 --> 00:11:44,627
and start a family.

274
00:11:45,467 --> 00:11:46,147
Let me tell you,

275
00:11:46,306 --> 00:11:47,587
people who seem like a playboy

276
00:11:47,747 --> 00:11:49,107
are actually the most loyal,

277
00:11:49,107 --> 00:11:50,107
most devoted.

278
00:11:50,546 --> 00:11:51,387
If he had

279
00:11:51,387 --> 00:11:52,267
no feelings for you,

280
00:11:52,347 --> 00:11:53,186
then why did he linger

281
00:11:53,267 --> 00:11:54,147
at the hotel entrance

282
00:11:54,426 --> 00:11:55,426
and not go in

283
00:11:55,467 --> 00:11:56,147
when you

284
00:11:56,147 --> 00:11:57,107
